# crypt -
# $Header$

= algorithm =
 * Digest/Hash: CRC, MD5(1991), SHA1
 * systemic: RC4, RC5, DES(1970s), AES(2001-11), BLOWFISH
 * non-systemic: RSA, DSA

= Terms =
 * cipher
 * code
 * plaintext
 * ciphertext
 * key
 * cryptology
 * substitution cipher
 * transposition cipher
 * one-time pad
 * symmetric-key algorithm
 * round
 *

= 两个密码学基本原则 =
 * 消息必须包含一定的冗余度
 * 需要采取某种方法来对抗重放攻击

